      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLACK NOIR (8) was in the placings last time but prior to that he posted an excellent 19.42 win over 342m at this track. Rates on top and can find winning form again. DAKOTA AVA (5) is going well, finishing in the placings twice in a row. Not beaten far last time when a 0.8 lengths third (30.66) in a Grade 5 at this track. Speedy runner who can find the front with a clear break off trap seven. Well placed here and can atone this time. VICTORY CLUB (2) drew an outside box and was game in defeat when only a nose from the winner Hi There Frank in second(30.85) at this track. Has good speed and a low draw is a big help. Expected to feature. MIDNIGHT SUN (1) has a solid strike rate from this box.",
